assert (HH : Par Q P Q Z).

Lemma onc2__oreq : forall A B C D P Q, InterCCAt A B C D P Q -> forall Z, OnCircle Z A B -> OnCircle Z C D -> Z=P \/ Z=Q.
assert(HCop := all_coplanar A C P Q).

apply(cop_onc2__oreq A B C D); assumption.
